sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App as Android App
    participant Google as Google Auth
    participant API as Backend API
    participant DB as MongoDB

    User ->> App: Sign in with Google
    App ->> Google: Request ID Token
    Google -->> App: ID Token

    App ->> API: Send ID Token
    API ->> Google: Verify ID Token
    Google -->> API: Token Valid

    API ->> DB: Find or Create User
    DB -->> API: User Record

    API ->> API: Generate JWT
    API -->> App: Access & Refresh Tokens

    App ->> API: Authenticated Requests
    API ->> API: verifyJWT Middleware
